39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">filter</strong>&nbsp;过滤器从数组中选择一个子集：</p><h2 class=\"example\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.4px; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(97, 127, 16); background-color: transparent;\">AngularJS 实例</h2><p><span class=\"highLT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"highELE\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">div</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"highATT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 204);\">ng-app=</span><span class=\"highVAL\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(170, 17, 17);\">&quot;myApp&quot;</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"highATT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 204);\">ng-controller=</span><span class=\"highVAL\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(170, 17, 17);\">&quot;namesCtrl&quot;</span><span class=\"highGT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&gt;</span><br/><br/><span class=\"highLT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"highELE\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">p</span><span class=\"highGT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&gt;</span><span class=\"highLT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"highELE\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">input</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"highATT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 204);\">type=</span><span class=\"highVAL\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(170, 17, 17);\">&quot;text&quot;</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"highATT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; paddi