&quot;hour &gt; 12&quot;</span><span class=\"highGT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&gt;</span>我是可见的。<span class=\"highLT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"highELE\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">/p</span><span class=\"highGT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&gt;</span><br/><br/><span class=\"highLT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"highELE\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">/div</span><span class=\"highGT\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 119, 0);\">&gt;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><table class=\"lamp\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 728px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><th style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 5px 10px 10px; font-size: 1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 34px;\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/images/lamp.jpg\" alt=\"Note\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 32px; width: 32px;\"/></th><td style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 10px 4px 0px; font-size: 1em;\">在下一个章节中，我们将为大家更多通过点击按钮来隐藏 HTML 元素的实例。</td></tr></tbody></table><hr style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); height: 1px; bord